1.	Install Node.js v6.11.1 from https://nodejs.org/en/download/releases/ for 64 bit windows OS

2.  npm install --global --production windows-build-tools

3.	Win64OpenSSL-1_0_1m is available in the following box file https://paypal.box.com/s/ggd99xt0rttzgdx9vsye095gac3vt9p6

4.	Win64OpenSSL-1_0_1m.exe has to be installed .Please install It in C:\OpenSSL-Win64

5.	Also set path to C:\OpenSSL-Win64;C:\OpenSSL-Win64\bin;C:\OpenSSL-Win64\include

6.  upgrade npm run the command npm install -g npm

7.	Finally run npm install bignum in command prompt make sure it runs without any errors
